Text.SourceString: Well, if it ain't a new face 'round here! Name's <NPCName>Slamet</>, friend.//<portrait=normal>I take care of all these lovely sea horses, I do.
Text.LocalizedString: Well, if it ain't a new face 'round here! Name's <NPCName>Slamet</>, friend.//<portrait=normal>I take care of all these lovely sea horses, I do.

Text.SourceString: Swing by sometime, and I'll show ya 'round with dis.
Text.LocalizedString: Swing by sometime, and I'll show ya 'round with dis.

Text.SourceString: Oh, ya gotta come see dis seahorse, friend! Ain't she a beauty?//<portrait=happy>Her scales, they shine like nothin' else! I'm tellin' ya, just takes yer breath away with dis one.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, ya gotta come see dis seahorse, friend! Ain't she a beauty?//<portrait=happy>Her scales, they shine like nothin' else! I'm tellin' ya, just takes yer breath away with dis one.

Text.SourceString: Now, some of dis little fella's been a bit stubborn, but we're gettin' there. Ya see, ya just gotta talk to 'em.//You listen real good, and they'll tell ya all ya need to know with dis one.
Text.LocalizedString: Now, some of dis little fella's been a bit stubborn, but we're gettin' there. Ya see, ya just gotta talk to 'em.//You listen real good, and they'll tell ya all ya need to know with dis one.

Text.SourceString: Hmm, seems like I've run out of seaweed for dis week's feed.//<portrait=normal>Gonna have to head out and gather some more. These sea horses, they love it fresh, ya know?
Text.LocalizedString: Hmm, seems like I've run out of seaweed for dis week's feed.//<portrait=normal>Gonna have to head out and gather some more. These sea horses, they love it fresh, ya know?

Text.SourceString: Oh, what's for dinner tonight? Let me think... How 'bout a nice sea kelp salad with some oyster sauce? Makes yer taste buds dance with dis one, it does.
Text.LocalizedString: Oh, what's for dinner tonight? Let me think... How 'bout a nice sea kelp salad with some oyster sauce? Makes yer taste buds dance with dis one, it does.

Text.SourceString: Weather's a bit turbulent today. Gonna have to keep an eye on dis. Sea horses can be a bit jumpy when it gets like dis.
Text.LocalizedString: Weather's a bit turbulent today. Gonna have to keep an eye on dis. Sea horses can be a bit jumpy when it gets like dis.

Text.SourceString: Weather's a bit turbulent today. Gonna have to keep an eye on dis. Sea horses can be a bit jumpy when it gets like dis.
Text.LocalizedString: Weather's a bit turbulent today. Gonna have to keep an eye on dis. Sea horses can be a bit jumpy when it gets like dis.

Text.SourceString: Ya ever try crab stew? Keeps ya warm on a turbulent day, it does.
Text.LocalizedString: Ya ever try crab stew? Keeps ya warm on a turbulent day, it does.

Text.SourceString: These sea horses, they're mighty particular 'bout what they eat. Can't just feed 'em anything, ya know.//Dis seaweed from the north? They go wild for it.
Text.LocalizedString: These sea horses, they're mighty particular 'bout what they eat. Can't just feed 'em anything, ya know.//Dis seaweed from the north? They go wild for it.

Text.SourceString: Got myself a bit of a scrape on the coral today. Nothin' serious, mind ya. Just a reminder to watch meself out there with dis. The sea can be tricky.
Text.LocalizedString: Got myself a bit of a scrape on the coral today. Nothin' serious, mind ya. Just a reminder to watch meself out there with dis. The sea can be tricky.

Text.SourceString: Dis storm comin' in? Makes the waves all wild-like. I'll have to batten down the stables, make sure the little ones are safe.
Text.LocalizedString: Dis storm comin' in? Makes the waves all wild-like. I'll have to batten down the stables, make sure the little ones are safe.

Text.SourceString: Aye, it's harvest time for the sea berries. Gonna have to make myself some jam.
Text.LocalizedString: Aye, it's harvest time for the sea berries. Gonna have to make myself some jam.

Text.SourceString: Been working on a new training technique with the sea horses.//<portrait=happy>Takes time, patience, and a whole lot of love, dis does. But it's worth it to see 'em flourish.
Text.LocalizedString: Been working on a new training technique with the sea horses.//<portrait=happy>Takes time, patience, and a whole lot of love, dis does. But it's worth it to see 'em flourish.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes, late at night, I like to sit by the shore and watch the stars. Makes ya feel a part of something bigger.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes, late at night, I like to sit by the shore and watch the stars. Makes ya feel a part of something bigger.

Text.SourceString: Dragons and sea horses ain't so different, ya know. They've both got that wild spirit, that fire in their eyes.
Text.LocalizedString: Dragons and sea horses ain't so different, ya know. They've both got that wild spirit, that fire in their eyes.

Text.SourceString: I wonder what it's like, farming on land. Planting seeds, watching them grow.
Text.LocalizedString: I wonder what it's like, farming on land. Planting seeds, watching them grow.

Text.SourceString: Dis King of ours, he's a generous one. Let me tend to his sea horses since I was just a boy.//<portrait=happy>He trusts me, he does, and that's a precious thing.
Text.LocalizedString: Dis King of ours, he's a generous one. Let me tend to his sea horses since I was just a boy.//<portrait=happy>He trusts me, he does, and that's a precious thing.

Text.SourceString: Water's getting warmer, it is. Creatures don't mind much, but makes me feel...I don't know...warm.
Text.LocalizedString: Water's getting warmer, it is. Creatures don't mind much, but makes me feel...I don't know...warm.

Text.SourceString: Dis chill in the water, it's settling in, ain't it? Sea horses seem to like it.
Text.LocalizedString: Dis chill in the water, it's settling in, ain't it? Sea horses seem to like it.

Text.SourceString: Every once in a while, I get a craving for jamu. Heard it's good for your health up there.
Text.LocalizedString: Every once in a while, I get a craving for jamu. Heard it's good for your health up there.

Text.SourceString: Land dwellers...your people, yeah...they have this dish, lodeh. Veggie goodness in a pot.//The flavor, it’s somethin' else, I tell ya.
Text.LocalizedString: Land dwellers...your people, yeah...they have this dish, lodeh. Veggie goodness in a pot.//The flavor, it’s somethin' else, I tell ya.

Text.SourceString: If there's one thing I wish the merfolk could make down here, it's cenil. Chewy little things, they are.
Text.LocalizedString: If there's one thing I wish the merfolk could make down here, it's cenil. Chewy little things, they are.

Text.SourceString: I've had beer once, and lemme tell ya, it made me feel all sorts of funny! Not in a good way, mind you.
Text.LocalizedString: I've had beer once, and lemme tell ya, it made me feel all sorts of funny! Not in a good way, mind you.

Text.SourceString: You know, I've been offered wine a few times, but every sip makes me feel like I've ridden the wildest sea horse. No thanks.
Text.LocalizedString: You know, I've been offered wine a few times, but every sip makes me feel like I've ridden the wildest sea horse. No thanks.

Text.SourceString: Having the whole place to meself is great, but there are nights where I wouldn't mind a bit of company over a bowl of lodeh.
Text.LocalizedString: Having the whole place to meself is great, but there are nights where I wouldn't mind a bit of company over a bowl of lodeh.

Text.SourceString: I've my sea horses for company, and they're good listeners. But there are days when a chatter with someone would be nice.
Text.LocalizedString: I've my sea horses for company, and they're good listeners. But there are days when a chatter with someone would be nice.

Text.SourceString: It's not that I mind being by myself...it's just that sometimes, in the quiet moments, you realize you're truly alone.
Text.LocalizedString: It's not that I mind being by myself...it's just that sometimes, in the quiet moments, you realize you're truly alone.

Text.SourceString: Heard there's a different kinda way you folks grow things up on land. How do you even water plants without the whole ocean?
Text.LocalizedString: Heard there's a different kinda way you folks grow things up on land. How do you even water plants without the whole ocean?

Text.SourceString: If I ever come up to land, reckon you could teach me a thing or two about farming without fins?
Text.LocalizedString: If I ever come up to land, reckon you could teach me a thing or two about farming without fins?

Text.SourceString: When you harvest, do you sing to your plants? Down here, the creatures have their own sort of melodies.
Text.LocalizedString: When you harvest, do you sing to your plants? Down here, the creatures have their own sort of melodies.

Text.SourceString: Hey there, friend! What's the tide bringing you to today?
Text.LocalizedString: Hey there, friend! What's the tide bringing you to today?

Text.SourceString: Ah, it's you again! Good to see your fins around, mate.
Text.LocalizedString: Ah, it's you again! Good to see your fins around, mate.

Text.SourceString: How's that land farming of yours coming along?
Text.LocalizedString: How's that land farming of yours coming along?

Text.SourceString: Sometimes, just floating with the current and takin' it easy is all you need.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes, just floating with the current and takin' it easy is all you need.

Text.SourceString: Don' push yerself too hard, eh? The ocean's vast, and there's time for everything.
Text.LocalizedString: Don' push yerself too hard, eh? The ocean's vast, and there's time for everything.

Text.SourceString: Once had to lead a big ol' school of mackerel away from some nasty rocks. Tricky business, but sure is rewarding.
Text.LocalizedString: Once had to lead a big ol' school of mackerel away from some nasty rocks. Tricky business, but sure is rewarding.

Text.SourceString: Back when I was just a nipper, before I got all caught up with the sea horses, I used to herd fish as well. Quite the challenge, that was.
Text.LocalizedString: Back when I was just a nipper, before I got all caught up with the sea horses, I used to herd fish as well. Quite the challenge, that was.

Text.SourceString: I'm glad I can focus on sea horses now. Two jobs no more. Heh heh!
Text.LocalizedString: I'm glad I can focus on sea horses now. Two jobs no more. Heh heh!

Text.SourceString: Nimbus thought he'd play a lil' hide-and-seek today. Spotted him hidin' right by the purple coral, cheeky fella.
Text.LocalizedString: Nimbus thought he'd play a lil' hide-and-seek today. Spotted him hidin' right by the purple coral, cheeky fella.

Text.SourceString: You remember young Coral? She's pickin' up that swirly dance I've been teachin' her. Proud of her, I am!
Text.LocalizedString: You remember young Coral? She's pickin' up that swirly dance I've been teachin' her. Proud of her, I am!

Text.SourceString: Nimbus, oh, he's got this thing for blue kelp. It's quite a sight, watching him chase after them!
Text.LocalizedString: Nimbus, oh, he's got this thing for blue kelp. It's quite a sight, watching him chase after them!

Text.SourceString: During my fish-herdin' times, I once led a bunch of glowfish through the Deep Sea. Quite an adventure!
Text.LocalizedString: During my fish-herdin' times, I once led a bunch of glowfish through the Deep Sea. Quite an adventure!

Text.SourceString: Herded my first school of fish when I was barely a tadpole. They taught me much about patience and understanding.
Text.LocalizedString: Herded my first school of fish when I was barely a tadpole. They taught me much about patience and understanding.

Text.SourceString: Noticed some new shimmerfin fish making their way here. Reckon it's a sign of the seasons shiftin'?
Text.LocalizedString: Noticed some new shimmerfin fish making their way here. Reckon it's a sign of the seasons shiftin'?

Text.SourceString: Ate lodeh yesterday. Bursting with flavors, it was.
Text.LocalizedString: Ate lodeh yesterday. Bursting with flavors, it was.

Text.SourceString: Nothin' perks you up like a good ol' sip of Jamu after a tiring day, eh? Clears the mind and soothes the soul.
Text.LocalizedString: Nothin' perks you up like a good ol' sip of Jamu after a tiring day, eh? Clears the mind and soothes the soul.

Text.SourceString: There's a rhythm to life here. Once you get the hang of it, everythin' just...clicks.
Text.LocalizedString: There's a rhythm to life here. Once you get the hang of it, everythin' just...clicks.

Text.SourceString: Chatted with <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> the other day. She's got some curious thoughts about talkin' to seahorses.
Text.LocalizedString: Chatted with <NPCName>Cho Oyu</> the other day. She's got some curious thoughts about talkin' to seahorses.

Text.SourceString: Been dabbling in a bit of stone carving lately. Bit tricky, but oh, it's a calm little pastime.
Text.LocalizedString: Been dabbling in a bit of stone carving lately. Bit tricky, but oh, it's a calm little pastime.

Text.SourceString: Took a moment today, just floated up top, watchin' the sun come up.//<portrait=happy>Times like these, well, they're a bit of magic, aren't they?
Text.LocalizedString: Took a moment today, just floated up top, watchin' the sun come up.//<portrait=happy>Times like these, well, they're a bit of magic, aren't they?

Text.SourceString: Had a dream last night, wanderin' those deep trenches way past our kingdom. Wonder what's hiding in those parts?
Text.LocalizedString: Had a dream last night, wanderin' those deep trenches way past our kingdom. Wonder what's hiding in those parts?
